      "content": "thanks but i dont think talking helps. i've tried. it's just the same thing over and over. like i'm just stuck in this cycle and there's no way out of it. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace and sleep is if i just didn't have to deal with any of this anymore. like if i could just exit.",
